VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)\bSELECT\s+[^\s]+\s+FROM\s+\((SELECT\s+.*\$.*)\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:%s|\?|:\w+|params=|execute\(
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects nested subqueries with user input, which can lead to SQL injection vulnerabilities if input is not parameterized.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for SQL Query: Subqueries with User Input.
